'''Adony Station''' was a small [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] outpost on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]
[[Jerne]], close to ancient ruins of the [[Jerni]]. Due to the machinations of [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]], during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] leaders [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] were led to believe that a powerful artifact known as the [[Eternity Crystal]] was hidden near Adong Station. As a result, Skywalker and Organa, supported by the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Meeka Reen]] and [[Gender/Legends|her]] guerrillas, [[Mission to Jerne|assaulted]] the station and [[Death/Legends|killed]] its contingent of Imperial troops.<ref name="dkd" />

